  "description": "Fix Markdown Rendering on Enrollment Subpage\n\nInvestigate and resolve markdown rendering issues on the http://localhost:1313/o-przedszkolu/zapisy/ (enrollment) subpage that are preventing content from displaying correctly.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify which markdown elements are not rendering properly (headings, lists, links, formatting, etc.)\n- Locate the source markdown file for the zapisy (enrollment) page\n- Fix syntax errors or incorrect markdown formatting in the source file\n- Verify proper configuration of markdown processor settings if needed\n- Ensure all content displays as intended after fixes\n- Test that links, images, and special formatting work correctly\n- Confirm the page renders consistently with other subpages on the site\n- Rebuild and verify changes at localhost:1313",
